00:36:50,620 --> 00:36:53,980
 Jesus loves you.

734
00:36:53,980 --> 00:36:56,500
 There is bad news, I'm sorry.

735
00:36:56,500 --> 00:37:06,940
 Romans 6 says, "For the wages of sin is death, but there is a free gift of eternal life."

736
00:37:06,940 --> 00:37:10,300
 For you fall short of the glory of God, just like me.

737
00:37:10,300 --> 00:37:16,340
 There is no difference between you and I, but you and I are justified freely by His

738
00:37:16,340 --> 00:37:17,700
 grace as a gift.

739
00:37:17,700 --> 00:37:19,980
 It's free.

740
00:37:19,980 --> 00:37:20,980
 It's free.

741
00:37:20,980 --> 00:37:22,860
 Receive it.

742
00:37:22,860 --> 00:37:25,260
 It's a simple gospel.

743
00:37:25,260 --> 00:37:27,020
 It's before and after.

744
00:37:27,020 --> 00:37:28,140
 It's dead, now alive.

745
00:37:28,140 --> 00:37:29,220
 It's blind, now see.

746
00:37:29,220 --> 00:37:31,420
 It's lost, now found.

747
00:37:31,420 --> 00:37:32,700
 It's simple.

748
00:37:32,700 --> 00:37:33,700
 Keep it simple.

749
00:37:33,700 --> 00:37:35,900
 Number two, that ties in.

750
00:37:35,900 --> 00:37:36,900
 Be clear.

751
00:37:36,900 --> 00:37:41,220
 Get to the point where you are able to share with the people that God has placed in front

752
00:37:41,220 --> 00:37:46,140
 of you and say, "This is the reason why I hope, because without Him, I was so lost.

753
00:37:46,140 --> 00:37:47,380
 I was overcome with worry.

754
00:37:47,380 --> 00:37:51,220
 I was overcome with hate and resentment, but because of Him, I am now freed from those

755
00:37:51,220 --> 00:37:52,220
 things."

756
00:37:52,780 --> 00:37:55,900
 And you can do it.

757
00:37:55,900 --> 00:37:58,620
 And share it with humility.

758
00:37:58,620 --> 00:38:06,380
 Too many people's idea of church is, "Oh, there's these condescending, old, judgmental

