00:38:09,980 --> 00:38:10,980
 Right?

761
00:38:10,980 --> 00:38:14,980
 "Do as I say."

762
00:38:14,980 --> 00:38:20,220
 But when the whole point of the gospel is that we are all sinners, you can share it

763
00:38:20,220 --> 00:38:22,500
 with this humble heart.

764
00:38:22,500 --> 00:38:25,660
 "Don't you worry.

765
00:38:25,660 --> 00:38:27,820
 I'm not judging you because I'm just as bad as you.

766
00:38:27,820 --> 00:38:29,380
 I can't reach the moon either.

767
00:38:29,380 --> 00:38:30,380
 Don't worry.

768
00:38:30,380 --> 00:38:33,580
 It's not as though I have some special hops that gets me to the moon.

769
00:38:33,580 --> 00:38:34,580
 No, no, no.

770
00:38:34,580 --> 00:38:35,580
 We're the same."

771
00:38:35,580 --> 00:38:39,500
 And that ties in with the vulnerability.

772
00:38:39,500 --> 00:38:44,300
 The way you proclaim the gospel is you just share with them how you heard the gospel,

